{
  "stem": "12684.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I found because-- [PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] let's come back for a little bit.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "During the time when we were there trying to stay alive they did the most heinous thing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were hanging people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We don't know what they did, but we had to watch it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is something very bad to watch when somebody is getting hanged.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this is how you learned to see it because people watched you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You had to watch it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You see it, and you didn't see it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And during that kind of happening I realized what they do-- what they try to do is to undermine your sanity in any way they could so that you either end up dead or a Muselman, as they call it, or incapable of doing anything, and they don't need to food you anymore.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Muselman means somebody who [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] walks like this, looks on the floor and is ready to die.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The mind is already about to die.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we decide-- you know, all the ones we knew, we decided to, to pep talk us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We saw it, but it's gone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's past.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Luckily we didn't know who it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this is how we sustained ourselves through that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And these were very, very difficult days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then they made a mistake, and they put us in the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we tried to protest, but, you know, you can't protest anything until-- we said we wanted to poll this person and that person, and Mengele, and ba ba ba, you know?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And finally they said, it is a mistake, and they opened the doors again.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And from that gas, which had already emitted, you were completely drowsy, and if you had asked me my name then I would have not known.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
